html.mdc-typography
  head
    title RolzPro AAW
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='material-components-web.css')
  main(class="mdc-typography")

    img(src='/RolzProLogo2.svg', alt='RolzPro.com Logo v1, (c) 2017 RolzPro.com')

    .mdc-card.getcard(style="max-width:500px")
      section.mdc-card__primary
        divc.mdc-typography--heading2
          |Good news! RolzPro AAW is switching account authentication hash to SHA512! What does this mean for you? SHA512 will secure and hash your passwords more safely than our previous standard, and it is the leading and proven most secure hash used today by all websites and account password systems. To take advantage of the SHA512 hashing, you must reeenter your password or change your password, to allow us to generate a new hash. This needs to be done by the user, because only you know your password, and an unsafe, unhashed version of your password is NOT stored in our databases or our knowledge. For more information on hashing and the SHA512 hash method, check these sites out:
          |   https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SHA-3
          |   https://www.wired.com/2016/06/hacker-lexicon-password-hashing/
    .mdc-card.getcard(style="max-width:500px")
      section.mdc-card__primary
        form#get-form(action='/confirmfromlegacypass', method='POST')
          div
            .mdc-form-field
              .mdc-textfield(data-mdc-auto-init='MDCTextfield')
                input#getid.mdc-textfield__input(type='password', name='pass')
                label.mdc-textfield__label(for='getid')
                  | Confirm Password
          button.mdc-button.mdc-button--raised.mdc-button--primary.mdc-ripple-surface(type='submit', data-mdc-auto-init='MDCRipple')
            | Submit and Continue to RolzPro AAW

    aside#mdc-dialog-with-list.mdc-dialog(style='visibility:hidden', role='alertdialog', aria-labelledby='mdc-dialog-with-list-label', aria-describedby='mdc-dialog-with-list-description')
      .mdc-dialog__surface
        header.mdc-dialog__header
          h2#mdc-dialog-with-list-label.mdc-dialog__header__title=loginerrormessage
        footer.mdc-dialog__footer
          button.mdc-button.mdc-dialog__footer__button.mdc-dialog__footer__button--cancel(type='button') Got It!
      .mdc-dialog__backdrop
    
    .mdc-card.getcard(style="max-width:500px")
      section.mdc-card__primary
        divc.mdc-typography--heading2 
          |For more info regarding our new 'Users FIRST' policy, please contact RolzPro technical support directly at cwu159@gmail.com.

  script(src='https://unpkg.com/material-components-web@latest/dist/material-components-web.min.js')
  script.
    window.mdc.autoInit();

  script.
    (function() {
      var swidth = screen.width;
      var sheight = screen.height;
      var wrongpass = !{JSON.stringify(wrongpass)};
      if(wrongpass=='true')
      {
        var dialogScrollable = new mdc.dialog.MDCDialog(document.querySelector('#mdc-dialog-with-list'));
        dialogScrollable.show();
      }
    })();